      "text": [
        " الرَّجُلِ يَتَزَوَّجُ الْبِكْرَ قَالَ يُقِيمُ عِنْدَهَا سَبْعَةَ أَيَّامٍ"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hisham Bin Salim, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> regarding the man who marries a virgin. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘He should stay with her for seven days’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "39. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘ Umayr from Hisham ibn Salim who has said the following: “About the case of a man who marries a virgin woman, abu ‘ Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘He must stay with her for seven days.’” "
        ]
      }
    }
